Mazel, 1979, Entomops, Nice 6: 267, figs 1, 2 (
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Zygaena" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zygaena" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="127" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Zygaena</taxonomicName>
